ow" title="Category:People from Glasgow">People from Glasgow</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Plagiarism_controversies" title="Category:Plagiarism controversies">Plagiarism controversies</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Social_democrats" title="Category:Social democrats">Social democrats</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:The_Huffington_Post_writers_and_columnists" title="Category:The Huffington Post writers and columnists">The Huffington Post writers and columnists</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:The_Independent_people" title="Category:The Independent people">The Independent people</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Writers_from_London" title="Category:Writers from London">Writers from London</a></li></ul></div><div id="mw-hidden-catlinks" class="mw-hidden-catlinks mw-hidden-cats-hidden">Hidden categories: <ul><li><a href="/wiki/Category:All_articles_with_dead_external_links" title="Category:All articles with dead external links">All articles with dead external links</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Articles_with_dead_external_links_from_September_2011" title="Category:Articles with dead external links from September 2011">Articles with dead external links from September 2011</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Articles_with_hCards" title="Category:Articles with hCards">Articles with hCards</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Commons_category_template_with_no_category_set" title="Category:Commons category template with no category set">Commons category template with no category set</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Commons_category_with_page_title_same_as_on_Wikidata" title="Category:Commons category with page title same as on Wikidata">Commons category with page title same as on Wikidata</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Use_dmy_dates_from_November_2013" title="Category:Use dmy dates from November 2013">Use dmy dates from November 2013</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Articles_with_inconsistent_citation_formats" title="Category:Articles with 